headline: 2 Reasons FOXA is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: FOX has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 13.8%. The stock now trades at $56.48, marking a 17.9% gain. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
